content.rendered:
Directed by Vijay Kumar Kalivarapu

Written by Vijay Kumar Kalivarapu

Star Suma Kanakala (Jayamma). Shalini Kondepudi (Anitha). Dinesh Kumar (Pujari Sathya Babu).Rest of cast listed alphabetically:. Bonela Asirayya (Jamukula Kunda). Siva Prasad Bandaru (Rambabu – Superintendent Of Police). Jyothi Bathula (Aadhemma). Rajesh Bendhalam (Naxal Sub Leader). Charmila (Sravanthi). Salana Chiranjivi (Minister’s Personal Assistant). Navvula Damodhar (Farmer). Amar Enni (Somi). Gautham (Elaka). Govindhamma (Padhma). D Hema (Indhamma). Rama Rao Jadhav (Naxal Leader). Vissu Jallu (Teacher 3). Naveen Jogi (Ambedhkar Association Member 1). Joy (Yesubabu). Chappa Krishna (Rami Naidu). Chinni Krishna (Teacher 2). Rajya Lakshmi (Sharadhamma). Naveen Lysetty (Photographer 1). Challa Mahesh (Shankar). Sai Bharat Manku (Travel Agent). Yashika Maulkar (Receptionist – Multispecialty Hospital). Chintha Appula Naidu (Pastor). Sheshapu Surya Narayana (Ward Member 2). Nikhitha (Pushpa). Paarthu (Tractor Simmi). Srinu Padala (Madhu). Ramadevi Pallam (Lakshmi). Devi Prasad (Gouru Naidu). Vishnu Priya (Junior Doctor 2 – Multispecialty Hospital). Sreekakulam Rajeswari (Janakamma). Amma Ramakrishna (Jagga Rao). T V Raman (Pala Apparao). Rammurthy (Ganapathi Babu). Bolla Lalitha Rani (Poornamma). Bammidi Krishna Rao (Minister). Elisetty Rammohan Rao (Appula Naidu). Jaada Prasad Rao (Rich Person). Maddi Sudhakar Rao (Ward Member 1). Munji Bhaskar Rao (Thief). Reddy Maheswar Rao (Sathyam Naidu). Srinivas Rao (Tractor Owner). Tirupati Rao (Constable 2). Veera Bhadra Rao (Quary Owner). Komali Raut (Small Child’s Mother). Pakki Ravindranath (Money Lender). Dharsith Sai (Vijay). Bhuvan Saluru (Paari Naidu). Srikanth Sana (Photographer 2). Sangamegha (Munjeti Muthyala naidu). Challa Shantharam (RMP Doctor). Balakrishna Shepena (Gopi). Simhachalam (Charika Narsimhulu). Srikanth (Jon). Jaami Srinu (Constable 1). Sai Supriya (Teacher 1). Vennela Suresh (Chuttam Siva). Kota Suryanarayana (Gudivada Thatha). Mayanand Thakur (Sillangi Surya Rao). Thanay (Junior Doctor 1 – Multispecialty Hospital). Moola Thathayya (Ramana). Gedhela Trinath (Jammudu). Praveen Uppada (Ambedhkar Association Member 2). Simmi Vanjaraapu (Auto Srinu). Gedda Varaprasad (Doctor). Aadhi Keshavulu Yadav (Vice President). Ganesh Yadav (President)

Language Telugu

Producers Balaga Prakash

Production Vennela Creations
